At Dr. Dangs Lab, we process over 100,000 lab reports daily, each triggering a cascade of events—notifications to patients, updates to medical records, billing operations, and analytics pipelines.

7
00:00:34,915 --> 00:00:40,168
Traditional request-response architectures couldn't handle this scale efficiently.

8
00:00:40,168 --> 00:00:44,002
Enter Apache Kafka and event-driven architecture.

